article.description: — Jamal Mashburn Jr. had 21 points as New Mexico rolled past Northern New Mexico 78-46 on Friday night.
article.headline: New Mexico routs Northern New Mexico 78-46
article.linkText: New Mexico routs Northern New Mexico 78-46
article.story: ALBUQUERQUE, N.M. -- — Jamal Mashburn Jr. had 21 points as New Mexico rolled past Northern New Mexico 78-46 on Friday night. Jaelen House had 10 points for New Mexico (10-14). Jay Allen-Tovar added 10 points. Sebastian Forsling had 10 rebounds. Tyrique Weaver had 18 points and seven rebounds for the Eagles. Ricardo Zambrano added 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
